# Phase 8: FAISS Integration Implementation Plan

This plan details the implementation of Phase 8, which is the final piece of the core RAG setup. We need to store the embedding vectors generated in Phase 7 into a persistent Vector Database so that we can search and retrieve them later. We will use FAISS (Facebook AI Similarity Search) via LangChain.

## User Review Required

Please review the proposed approach for integrating FAISS.
> [!IMPORTANT]
> I propose creating a `VectorStoreManager` class in `src/vector_store.py`. This module will manage the FAISS index, persisting it to the `vectorstore/` directory on disk so that uploaded PDFs remain available across app restarts. We will use the existing `EmbeddingEngine` to supply the vectors.

